 dish, and fish on Varoma tray."},{"content":"Place Varoma into position then steam <b>4-5 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Meanwhile, place mooli in a bowl and cover with a little dressing, turning it to coat."},{"content":"Remove Varoma and keep covered. Warm remaining dressing in a small saucepan on the hob."},{"content":"To serve, place 3 pieces of mullet in a deep plate, with 3 tortelloni. Place the mooli 'spaghetti' in the centre of each plate. Garnish with coriander shoots and drizzle the warm dressing around."}],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","5h","6 portions"]}